42#ifndef _AMU_H
43#define _AMU_H
44
45/*
46 * Decide what maximum level of NFS server to try and mount with.
47 */
48#if defined(HAVE_FS_NFS4)
49# define NFS_VERS_MAX NFS_VERSION4
50#elif defined(HAVE_FS_NFS3)
51# define NFS_VERS_MAX NFS_VERSION3
52#else /* not HAVE_FS_NFS3 */
53# define NFS_VERS_MAX NFS_VERSION
54#endif /* not HAVE_FS_NFS3 */
55# define NFS_VERS_MIN NFS_VERSION
56
57/* some systems like ncr2 do not define this in <rpcsvc/mount.h> */
58#ifndef MNTPATHLEN
59# define MNTPATHLEN 1024
60#endif /* not MNTPATHLEN */
61#ifndef MNTNAMLEN
62# define MNTNAMLEN 255
63#endif /* not MNTNAMLEN */
64
65/*
66 * external definitions for building libamu.a
67 */
68extern voidp amqproc_null_1(voidp argp, CLIENT *rqstp);
69extern amq_mount_tree_p *amqproc_mnttree_1(amq_string *argp, CLIENT *rqstp);
70extern voidp amqproc_umnt_1(amq_string *argp, CLIENT *rqstp);
71extern amq_mount_stats *amqproc_stats_1(voidp argp, CLIENT *rqstp);
72extern amq_mount_tree_list *amqproc_export_1(voidp argp, CLIENT *rqstp);
73extern int *amqproc_setopt_1(amq_setopt *argp, CLIENT *rqstp);
74extern amq_mount_info_list *amqproc_getmntfs_1(voidp argp, CLIENT *rqstp);
75extern int *amqproc_mount_1(voidp argp, CLIENT *rqstp);
76extern amq_string *amqproc_getvers_1(voidp argp, CLIENT *rqstp);
77
78extern long get_server_pid(void);
79
80#endif /* not _AMU_H */
